                                "text": "I like the idea of hybridizing an open-ended canvas with a focused view mode, but it isn’t clear from this video how your system does that. The drag-out interaction looks indistinguishable from clicking on hyperlink. Do the dragged-out links appear on the canvas when you switch out of focused mode? Etc."
